title: Lottery announces big wins in Eau Claire | Local Briefs | leadertelegram.com
text: EAU CLAIRE — Eau Claire has a new millionaire, according to the Wisconsin Lottery. Vasil Kapbardhi claimed a $1 million Super Millions prize on Wednesday, beating the one-in-160,000 odds.
